{
    "chapter": 69,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "69:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主陈述对万物都将实现的复活时刻，</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "69:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后祂以这样一个问题增加该事件的重大性；什么是灾难呢？</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "69:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你怎么知道这灾难是什么呢？</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "69:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>萨利赫的宗族赛莫德人和胡德的宗族阿德人否认了那恐惧、令人惊悚的复活日，</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "69:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>至于赛莫德人，真主以极为恐惧和严厉的雷鸣毁灭了他们，</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "69:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>至于阿德人，真主以极寒的、对于他们极为严厉的飓风毁灭了他们。</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "69:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主派遣那风狂刮了七夜八昼彻底将他们毁灭，你看到整个族人都倒立在自己家里地上，他们被毁灭后的情景好像坠落到地上已腐烂的椰枣壳。</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "69:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你能看到惩罚后他们还有一个活口存留吗？</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "69:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>法老和他之前的古人，以及被倾覆惩罚的许多村落-即鲁特的族人们，他们再次以匹配和作恶犯罪，</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "69:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们都违抗和否认被派至他们的使者，故真主在毁灭他们之后再次惩罚了他们。</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "69:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当洪水泛过其最高极限时，我使你们乘上奴哈依我的命令制造的那只航行的船，那船是承载你们的，</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "69:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以便我使那船舶及其故事成为求证毁灭不信道者、拯救信士者的一种借鉴，</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "69:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当掌管吹号角的天使吹响一声号角时，那是第二次号角声，</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "69:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>大地和众山被升起，两者相互剧烈碰撞一次，大地和众山的碎片散布开来，</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "69:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在这些大事发生之日就是复活日，</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "69:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那日，天空裂开，众天使从空中降下，曾经坚固的天空在那日变得脆弱，</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "69:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>众天使在天空的边际和各方，在那个重大的日子，临近真主的八位天使担负着你的主的阿尔西。</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "69:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！那日，你们将被陈列在真主面前，你们的丝毫事情都不能隐瞒于真主，真主是全观一切的，</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "69:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>用右手接受功过薄的人，快乐和愉悦地说：“你们拿我的功过薄读读吧！</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "69:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在今世，我确信自己将被复活，接受我的报酬。”</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "69:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他将看见永久的恩泽而沐浴在愉悦的生活中，</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "69:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在那高位的乐园里，</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "69:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>其果实对于采摘者是临近的，</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "69:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有个声音对他们尊敬地说：“你们吃、饮这些毫无伤害的饮食吧！这是你们在今世曾经的岁月里，所行善功的回赐。”</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "69:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>用左手接受功过薄的人，他极度懊悔地说：“但愿我没有接受我的功过薄，其中全是应受惩罚的恶行。</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "69:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>但愿我对自己的清算毫不知情！</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "69:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>但愿我曾经的死亡是之后永不再复活的死亡，</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "69:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的钱财没有为我阻止真主的丝毫惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "69:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我曾经依靠的权力和情份的托辞离我远去。”</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "69:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有个声音说：“天使们啊！逮住他！把他的手放回他的脖子上，</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "69:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后把他投进火里去遭受火刑，</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "69:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后，把他装到七十臂长的铁链上，</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "69:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他曾不相信伟大真主，</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "69:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>不勉励他人赈济穷人。</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "69:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>今天，他没有任何亲戚为他阻挡惩罚。”</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "69:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>除火狱居民流出的脓汁外，他没有可食的食物，</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "69:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>只有犯罪和作恶者食那食物，</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "69:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以你们所能看见的盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "69:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以你们所不能看见的盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "69:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>《古兰经》是真主的语言，由祂尊敬的使者向人们宣读，</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "69:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>它不是诗人的话语，因为它不是依循诗歌的韵律，你们很少信仰，</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "69:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>它不是卜者的话语，因为卜者的话有别于这部《古兰经》，你们很少觉悟，</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "69:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>《古兰经》是降示自万物的主宰，</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "69:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>假若穆罕默德以我的名义捏造了我没有说过的话，</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "69:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我必惩罚他，必以权力和能力逮捕他，</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "69:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>然后，必割断连接心脏的动脉，</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "69:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们任何人都不能阻止我，他绝不会因为你们而以我的名义捏造，</p>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "69:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>《古兰经》是遵循真主命令和远离其禁戒的敬畏者的借鉴。</p>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "69:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确知道你们中否认这《古兰经》的人，</p>"
        },
        "50": {
            "verses": {
                "69:50": {
                    "id": 50
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>否认《古兰经》在复活日是巨大的悔恨，</p>"
        },
        "51": {
            "verses": {
                "69:51": {
                    "id": 51
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>《古兰经》确是毫无质疑的、来自真主的确凿的真理。</p>"
        },
        "52": {
            "verses": {
                "69:52": {
                    "id": 52
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！故你当赞美你的主超越所有不符合祂的描述，你当赞美你的主的美名。</p>"
        }
    }
}